    "all_cash": "NA",
    "additional_note": "NA",
    "cshoc": 46810000,
    "comments_1": "On March 26, a board meeting discussed \"the lack of interest from financial buyers in light of the company\u2019s recent financial performance and the potential difficulties this created for financial buyers to use debt to finance a purchase of the company, and the fact that strategic buyers would likely attribute the greatest value to the company and its business... it was in the best interests of the company and its shareholders to confidentially approach strategic buyers that the board believed would be most likely to have interest in a potential acquisition of the company to explore their interest, but to also further conduct a limited confirmatory exploration of interest of financial buyers.\"",
